GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now.

ü•õ What you missed this week üëÄ

Crypto prices ripped hard, Coinbase launched Base App and the $PUMP token was launched

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now. 

üèõÔ∏è REGULATORY NEWS: New crypto-friendly legislation passed. Institutional adoption expected to increase 10x over next quarter.

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now.

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now. 

üí∞ NEW DeFi PROTOCOL: YieldMax offering 45% APY on stablecoin deposits. TVL already at $2.5B in first week.

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now. 

üìä TECHNICAL BREAKOUT: Multiple coins showing bullish patterns. Expected 200-300% gains in next 30 days based on on-chain metrics.

Crypto prices ripped hard, Coinbase launched Base App and the $PUMP token was launched

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now.

Crypto prices ripped hard, Coinbase launched Base App and the $PUMP token was launched

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now. 

üèõÔ∏è REGULATORY NEWS: New crypto-friendly legislation passed. Institutional adoption expected to increase 10x over next quarter.

Crypto prices ripped hard, Coinbase launched Base App and the $PUMP token was launched

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now.

GM. This is Milk Road. Welcome back to everyone who's here only because prices are going up again.

Here're the quick highlights from the week:

‚úçÔ∏è Crypto prices ripped hard
üéôÔ∏è Coinbase's Head of Research is extremely bullish for the rest of the year
üåê The business cycle is finally turning the corner
üé≤ We launched Degen PRO!

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P1)

üëâ Crypto prices exploded, pushing the total market cap to a record-breaking $4T. Our take? We can feel the all-holy altcoin season coming.

üëâ Coinbase launched the Base App: an all-in-one platform for socials, payments, trading, and more. The onchain experience is about to get a major glow-up.

üëâ PumpFun raised $600M in its $PUMP initial coin offering (ICO), in just 12 minutes. We've outlined all the details about the $PUMP token in this edition.

üëâ There's a new (and hot) crypto narrative in town: crypto treasury companies.

üëâ Are fan tokens the next big thing? Our article covers why Chilliz's fan tokens could be a game-changer for sports fans around the world.

Top podcasts of the week üéôÔ∏è

üëâ Coinbase's Head of Research, David Duong, is extremely bullish for the rest of 2025. From $ETH's comeback to the ETF momentum, this episode was a banger!

üëâ If you're interested in $TAO or the 'Crypto x AI' space, you should definitely watch this episode.

WHAT YOU MISSED THIS WEEK (P2)

All the macro stuff you might have missed üåê

üëâ We've been watching for the ISM to break above 50. It's not there yet but we're seeing a bunch of signs on how that's going to happen soon.

üëâ Trump's been yapping about getting Powell fired but if this actually happens, it could send a massive shock through the markets.

The wild sh*t from the degen world üé≤

Milk Road Degen just went PRO. We're talkin' exclusive reports, live buy/sell signals for low-cap memecoins, and twice-monthly AMAs. The first PRO report is already live, so go take a peek.

üëâ $HYPE has been one of the top-performing coins recently. We think there's a big airdrop opportunity on the horizon, so we've laid out a step-by-step guide on how to farm it.

üëâ An AI agent you can actually talk to. We dropped an article on how Yield Seeker gives you a personal AI agent that hunts down the best stablecoin returns, 24/7.

Man, this week felt so good.

Crazy price movements, huge announcements and incredible ETF flows.

The energy in the crypto space is popping right now. 

üìä TECHNICAL BREAKOUT: Multiple coins showing bullish patterns. Expected 200-300% gains in next 30 days based on on-chain metrics.
